&quot;In any case, I doubt that it will be as valuable after tomorrow. We found a bug with the way &quot;haste&quot; items stack with &quot;haste&quot; spells. Basically, even the worst haste item combined with the worst haste spell would put the wearer at the haste cap. This basically invalidated the better haste items and spells, and explains why people have been saying that the newer haste items aren't any better than the FBSS. <br>
